@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/reviews

### Get user's reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get reviewable order items (delivered + paid, not yet reviewed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviewable
Content-Type: application/json

### Create a review (replace with real orderId and orderItemId from reviewable endpoint)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
  "orderId": "6a342ecb89921bcf30a04e09",
  "orderItemId": "6a342ecb89921bcf30a04e0a",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Great product!"
}
